Update Mirrors and System;
  
sudo apt update     - update archives
sudo apt upgrade    - update packages

to only upgrade package (dont use chrome) - sudo apt-get install --only-upgrade google-chrome-stable 

sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade - update all
 *if this dont work use this - sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y


Errors;

For audio driver/device  not detecting... kill audioprocess -   pulseaudio -k
and run pulseaudio again 

for network not detecting graphically disable LAN or Wifi and reconnect or Restart network



Cleaning;

apt autoclean
apt autoremove

or *Use bleachbit app for graphical way;

       sudo apt install bleachbit
